      <description><![CDATA[<p>Mariana and Gus look at Disney's SECOND EVER animated movie (<em>Pinocchio</em>) and its not-so-great-but-better-than-Snow-White 2022 remake (also called <em>Pinocchio</em>).</p><p></p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://patreon.com/OnceMoreWithFeeling?utm_medium=unknown&amp;utm_source=join_link&amp;utm_campaign=creatorshare_creator&amp;utm_content=copyLink">Support us! (Patreon)</a></p><p></p><p>Follow Us!</p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.instagram.com/withfeelingpod">IG</a></p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@withfeelingpod">TikTok</a></p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://bsky.app/profile/withfeelingpod.bsky.social">Bluesky</a></p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCc6JIvM541_Gufq_VYYauMQ">YouTube</a></p><p></p><p>Once More With Feeling is a podcast about great original movies and their often not-so-great remakes. Join film critic and YouTuber Mariana Colín (<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.youtube.com/@themorbidzoo">The Morbid Zoo</a>) and screenwriter and comedian Gus Schiff as they explore the history, culture, and politics of some of Hollywood's favorite films to make over and over and over and over and over…</p><p>Music by: Isaiah Evans (<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.instagram.com/the_viennese_school?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet&amp;igsh=ZDNlZDc0MzIxNw==">@the_viennese_school</a>) </p><p>Singing by: Sierra Lancaster (<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.instagram.com/_sierralancaster_/">@_sierralancaster_</a>)</p><p></p><p>Email: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="mailto:withfeelingpod@gmail.com">withfeelingpod@gmail.com</a></p>]]></description>
