      <title><![CDATA[Once More With Poisoned Apples - Snow White (1937 & 2025)]]></title>
      <itunes:title><![CDATA[Once More With Poisoned Apples - Snow White (1937 & 2025)]]></itunes:title>
      <description><![CDATA[<p>Join film critic and YouTuber Mariana Colín (<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.youtube.com/@themorbidzoo">The Morbid Zoo</a>) and screenwriter and comedian Gus Schiff as they dive into the Disney vaults to talk about the seminal classic SNOW WHITE AND THE SEVEN DWARFS (1937) and how time, culture, and greed made SNOW WHITE (2025) such a flaming pile of not very good movie.</p><p></p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://patreon.com/OnceMoreWithFeeling?utm_medium=unknown&amp;utm_source=join_link&amp;utm_campaign=creatorshare_creator&amp;utm_content=copyLink">Support us!</a></p><p>Follow us!</p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.instagram.com/withfeelingpod">IG</a></p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@withfeelingpod">TikTok</a></p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://bsky.app/profile/withfeelingpod.bsky.social">Bluesky</a></p><p></p><p>Once More With Feeling is a podcast about great original movies and their often not-so-great remakes. Join film critic and YouTuber Mariana Colín (<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.youtube.com/@themorbidzoo">The Morbid Zoo</a>) and screenwriter and comedian Gus Schiff as they explore the history, culture, and politics of some of Hollywood's favorite films to make over and over and over and over and over…</p><p>Music by: Isaiah Evans (<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.instagram.com/the_viennese_school?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet&amp;igsh=ZDNlZDc0MzIxNw==">@the_viennese_school</a>) </p><p>Singing by: Sierra Lancaster (<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.instagram.com/_sierralancaster_/">@_sierralancaster_</a>)</p><p></p><p>Email: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="mailto:withfeelingpod@gmail.com">withfeelingpod@gmail.com</a></p>]]></description>
